Cyber Claw:





Cyber Claw murmurings inside a near-by door. He focused her ears on it, and 
attempted to listen in. She heard one female voice and a few male voice. One 
she recongized as Rhinox. Now that there was Rhinox, she had to find 
Optimus. She walked closer to the door and arched her neck to it. She 
uttered a musing sound with a deep voice.
